summary: An ordinance relating to the improvement of The Alley between Blocks 3 and 4, Central Park Addition to West Seattle, being the Alley between 44th Avenue Southwest and 45th Avenue Southwest from West Alaska Street to West Edmunds Street, and certain other alleys, streets and avenues, by paving and otherwise improving the same, Local Improvement District No. 6004, and appropriating money from the City Street Fund in aid thereof.
